Wednesday, April 13, 1994

MERIT DOCKET

94-298. State ex rel. Crane v. Judges, Court of Appeals of Ohio, Columbiana Cty.

In Procedendo. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., AW. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
